Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Falklands casualties
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wvmm
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 9 May 1982
Falklands naval casualties leave Reagan's warship plans under scrutiny. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less